name: auction_of_names
prompt: Names are no longer assigned at birth but sold at auction. Write an auctioneer’s speech as they present a name everyone wants.
decoded: Ladies and gentlemen, I am thrilled to present to you a name that has captured the hearts of many. This name is not just a title, but a legacy, a story, and a dream. Please bid, and let's see who will be the first to claim this precious name. Let's begin!
